comments: Millsap (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Young (IND).

Matthews (IND) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Millsap (DEN) after the screen and absorbs the contact.

Barton (DEN) makes contact with Bogdanovic's (IND) arm during the rip-through and affects his SQBR.
Young (IND) sets the screen on Barton (DEN) and does not deliver contact.

Millsap (DEN) makes contact with Turner's (IND) arm and affects his shot attempt.

Barton (DEN) makes incidental high-five contact with Bogdanovic (IND) after he releases his jump shot attempt.
